Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.90,0:00:14.93,Show Title,,0,0,0,,{\fs142.5\fnGallow Tree\4aFF\pos(443.949,598.286)}KAMEN RIDER
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.15,0:00:15.24,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Shocker is coming,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.78,0:00:18.87,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,with its armies straight from hell
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.45,0:00:23.12,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Their black shadows threaten us all
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.12,0:00:26.75,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,but I'll fight to maintain\Nthe peace of our world!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.75,0:00:30.42,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Go! Go! Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.42,0:00:34.05,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,With my shining machine...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.05,0:00:36.80,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider Jump!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.72,0:00:40.27,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.35,0:00:45.02,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider, Kamen Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.02,0:00:48.65,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider, Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.65,0:00:51.15,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider Jump!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.28,0:00:54.95,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.86,0:00:59.49,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider, Kamen Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.49,0:01:03.16,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider, Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.50,0:01:11.14,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Ichimonji Hayato is the\NKamen Rider, a cyborg.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.14,0:01:15.13,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He was modified by the evil Shocker, a secret\Norganization plotting world domination.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.13,0:01:18.83,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider has pledged to fight\NShocker and free humanity!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.95,0:01:21.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Get back here!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.58,0:01:23.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Get back here!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.70,0:01:25.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Get back here!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.86,0:01:27.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Get back here!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.64,0:01:41.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider Fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.66,0:01:43.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Forgive us!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.79,0:01:45.39,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll be good from now on!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.39,0:01:46.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I surrender!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.86,0:01:48.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I surrender!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.70,0:01:51.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider's just so cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.24,0:01:54.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Time for me to be Rider now!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.59,0:01:55.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Nuh-uh! It's me!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.97,0:01:57.00,Default,,0,0,0,,It's me!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.00,0:02:00.68,Default,,0,0,0,,No. You said I could\Nbe Rider all day today.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.68,0:02:03.36,Default,,0,0,0,,It's no fun being Shocker all the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.36,0:02:04.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I wanna switch.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.93,0:02:05.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's switch!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.80,0:02:06.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, let's switch!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.26,0:02:09.10,Default,,0,0,0,,No way! Nyah!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.10,0:02:12.28,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not fair! Wait up!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.28,0:02:13.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait up!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.24,0:02:21.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait up!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.24,0:02:22.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold up, there.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.66,0:02:26.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.29,0:02:30.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like you're fans\Nof the Kamen Rider, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.56,0:02:32.43,Default,,0,0,0,,You bet we are!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.43,0:02:33.49,Default,,0,0,0,,That's great!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.96,0:02:35.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Why don't I
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.85,0:02:37.76,Default,,0,0,0,,take you to meet the real Kamen Rider?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.76,0:02:39.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.10,0:02:40.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you know the Kamen Rider?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.58,0:02:43.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't just know him.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.52,0:02:45.57,Default,,0,0,0,,We're very good friends!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.36,0:02:48.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Let us meet him!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.18,0:02:50.29,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.23,0:02:52.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Then I'll take you to meet him.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.52,0:02:56.69,Default,,0,0,0,,But if we stay out too long,\NMom is gonna be worried...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.46,0:02:58.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't force you to come.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.08,0:03:02.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.07,0:03:03.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Me, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.92,0:03:06.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Fine, I'll go, too...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.67,0:03:10.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, go on in.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.53,0:03:26.54,NEP AND TITLE,,0,0,0,,{\fscx100\fs185\bord0\fnCienfuegos\4aFF\b1\pos(537.167,690.389)}Monster School
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.53,0:03:26.54,NEP AND TITLE,,0,0,0,,{\fscx100\fs185\bord0\fnCienfuegos\4aFF\b1\pos(467.167,170.389)}Mukadelas'
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.94,0:03:29.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Nao!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.75,0:03:30.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Toshihiko!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.85,0:03:31.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Kiyo!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.98,0:03:33.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Toshihiko!\NNao!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.03,0:03:37.11,Default,,0,0,0,,That bike!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.89,0:03:44.20,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't think they\Nwere kidnapped, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.72,0:03:45.87,Default,,0,0,0,,What an awful thought...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.13,0:03:49.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Nao!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.17,0:03:55.34,Default,,0,0,0,,We get to meet the real Kamen Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.34,0:03:56.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna get his autograph.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.75,0:03:58.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I hope we get there soon!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.11,0:04:02.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it very far away?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.25,0:04:05.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Worried, are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.56,0:04:08.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I can show you the Kamen\NRider now, if you like.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.30,0:04:12.68,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Is he in this car?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.67,0:04:17.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Look behind you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.51,0:04:27.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Your cries won't save you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.18,0:04:30.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Just do as I say, and you'll\Nall meet the Kamen Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.58,0:04:40.67,Default,,0,0,0,,My darling students. Remain calm.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.97,0:04:48.64,Default,,0,0,0,,My powerful hypnosis was gifted to me\Nby the brilliant scientists of Shocker!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.57,0:04:59.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Mukadelas, I have your second directive.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.46,0:05:03.43,Default,,0,0,0,,What is the second directive, Colonel Zol?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.38,0:05:08.78,Default,,0,0,0,,The computer has chosen the next child\Nfor the Mukadelas Monster School.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.37,0:05:12.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Her name is Namie Ikusawa.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.04,0:05:16.19,Default,,0,0,0,,She's a brilliant student,\Njust like those four.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.97,0:05:39.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder if Goro's still studying...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.11,0:05:42.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I've gotta work just as hard as he does!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.57,0:05:59.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Nami?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.73,0:06:01.73,Default,,0,0,0,,What in the...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.97,0:06:04.34,Default,,0,0,0,,"Don't let Goro beat you"?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.47,0:06:09.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Look alive!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.53,0:06:10.60,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.65,0:06:12.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa, calm down!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.85,0:06:14.00,Default,,0,0,0,,What's with you, Goro?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.26,0:06:17.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you forget your homework and\Nget a lecture from your teacher?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.78,0:06:18.85,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.97,0:06:22.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.32,0:06:26.77,Default,,0,0,0,,G-Goro!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.27,0:06:30.56,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong with that kid?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.56,0:06:33.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Better to let sleeping dogs lie.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.64,0:06:36.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Apparently his little girlfriend\Ndidn't come to school today.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.65,0:06:37.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Didn't come to school?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.85,0:06:40.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Apparently she's a bit of a rival, too...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.28,0:06:42.05,Default,,0,0,0,,They're always competing for\Nthe best grade in class.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.05,0:06:43.69,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a bit concerning...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.69,0:06:45.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Why so, Ichimonji?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.10,0:06:46.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Look at this newspaper.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.67,0:06:47.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.43,0:06:55.60,Default,,0,0,0,,"Young Students Disappearing Across Japan"?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.60,0:06:58.71,Default,,0,0,0,,"All of the missing students\Nhad excellent grades."
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.71,0:07:00.60,Default,,0,0,0,,"Grieving parents left behind"...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.22,0:07:04.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't imagine what Shocker\Nwould want with young children...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.05,0:07:05.53,Default,,0,0,0,,But we can't rule it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.53,0:07:07.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, are you serious?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.28,0:07:10.32,Default,,0,0,0,,The new Shocker commander, Colonel Zol...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.91,0:07:15.83,Default,,0,0,0,,He does have a history of using children\Nfor his Near and Middle East campaign.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.62,0:07:17.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, dear...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.92,0:07:19.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Attention, boys and girls.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.31,0:07:24.63,Default,,0,0,0,,You've all been chosen for\Nyour incredible intelligence.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.61,0:07:28.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Soon, the world will belong to Shocker.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.27,0:07:33.80,Default,,0,0,0,,When that time comes, you will be the\Nleaders for boys and girls your age.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.75,0:07:41.40,Default,,0,0,0,,You require a special education\Nto give you what you need
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.40,0:07:43.65,Default,,0,0,0,,to be Junior Shocker leaders.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.64,0:07:46.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Those classes will begin today.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.67,0:07:51.05,Default,,0,0,0,,First, swear your loyalty to Shocker!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.33,0:07:57.11,Default,,0,0,0,,For the glory of the great Shocker!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.13,0:08:01.08,Default,,0,0,0,,For the glory of the great Shocker!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.86,0:08:06.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Let class begin!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.11,0:08:11.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Your first subject will be\Nthe proper handling of bombs.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.48,0:08:27.55,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.60,0:08:32.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Colonel, I wish to recommend\Na member for Junior Shocker.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.54,0:08:33.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Who is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.61,0:08:36.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Ishikura Goro, my friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.48,0:08:37.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Ishikura Goro?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.43,0:08:42.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder where Namie went off to...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.88,0:08:46.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Her Mom and Dad are so worried, darn it...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.40,0:08:51.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Goro!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.90,0:08:53.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, it's Namie!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.67,0:08:55.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Namie!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.57,0:08:56.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Goro!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.84,0:08:58.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Namie!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.01,0:08:59.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Goro!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.29,0:09:00.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Namie!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.83,0:09:06.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Taxi!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.12,0:09:12.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll pay later!\NJust follow that car, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.97,0:09:27.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Namie!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.61,0:09:30.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Namie! Namie!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.96,0:09:31.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.24,0:09:42.33,Default,,0,0,0,,That's weird... she was\Nthere just a minute ago...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.68,0:09:45.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Goro, get away!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.29,0:10:25.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't believe they came after me...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.80,0:10:30.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, what's that sound?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.10,0:10:37.14,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll never find me!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.14,0:10:39.60,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't escape me, brat!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.60,0:10:42.77,Default,,0,0,0,,You will join Junior Shocker!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.14,0:10:46.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Help!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.56,0:10:52.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Ishikura Goro.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.23,0:10:56.21,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll have special uses for you\Nas a member of Junior Shocker.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.21,0:10:57.58,Default,,0,0,0,,For instance...!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.25,0:11:00.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Shocker cyborg...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.14,0:11:02.75,Default,,0,0,0,,The name is Mukadelas.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.75,0:11:05.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Ichimonji Hayato!\NYou fell right into our trap.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.25,0:11:07.32,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.12,0:11:09.23,Default,,0,0,0,,What trap?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.68,0:11:13.98,Default,,0,0,0,,We know that wherever this boy goes, Kamen\NRider and his allies aren't far behind.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.98,0:11:18.40,Default,,0,0,0,,We used him as bait in our plan\Nto destroy Shocker's enemies!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.83,0:11:21.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.17,0:11:23.24,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you going to do\Nto those innocent children?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.24,0:11:27.02,Default,,0,0,0,,They're undergoing special training\Nas members of Junior Shocker!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.84,0:11:29.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Special training?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.37,0:11:32.94,Default,,0,0,0,,In Colonel Zol's Monster School.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.94,0:11:34.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Ichimonji Hayato...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.29,0:11:36.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Behold the power of Mukadelas!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.33,0:11:40.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't make me laugh...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.57,0:11:56.13,Default,,0,0,0,,You won't escape!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.13,0:11:58.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Have a shot of my\Nbrain-melting radio waves,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.50,0:12:00.49,Default,,0,0,0,,and die in agony!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.60,0:12:25.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Goro...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.31,0:12:32.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Not good... it's tearing\Nmy brain cells apart!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.67,0:12:35.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Transform!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.93,0:12:55.88,Bumper Episode 14-51,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fs85\pos(311,454)}KAMEN RIDER
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.98,0:13:13.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Goro!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.88,0:13:16.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.91,0:13:35.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Taki! Get on, hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.70,0:13:38.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.23,0:13:51.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider... I've prepared a\Nmore suitable opponent for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.95,0:14:01.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider! That's Gebacondor!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.69,0:14:04.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Damnable Shocker... They brought\NGebacondor back to life?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.03,0:14:46.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Sarracenian...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.52,0:15:03.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider, I lost sight of the car Goro was in!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.80,0:15:07.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Colonel Zol.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.24,0:15:11.01,Default,,0,0,0,,When will Junior Shocker begin\Nits campaign of destruction?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.53,0:15:15.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I believe they have reached a\Nsuitable place in their training.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.74,0:15:21.65,Default,,0,0,0,,The Shocker 190-type automatic\Nrifle allows for 24-round bursts
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.65,0:15:24.87,Default,,0,0,0,,and is effective at a range of 1500 meters.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.87,0:15:29.24,Default,,0,0,0,,This Shocker 205-type automatic\Nrifle comes with an infrared scope,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.24,0:15:34.80,Default,,0,0,0,,allows for 32-round bursts, and is\Neffective at a range of 2000 meters.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.80,0:15:37.42,Default,,0,0,0,,These are Shocker's most powerful rifles.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.58,0:15:51.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Next!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.58,0:16:01.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Explosives, sniper rifles, toxins...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.43,0:16:05.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Having mastered all of\Nthese things, tomorrow,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.02,0:16:08.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Junior Shocker will begin spreading\Ndestruction all over Japan.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.07,0:16:12.57,Default,,0,0,0,,No one will ever believe\Nthat children are behind this.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.97,0:16:14.62,Default,,0,0,0,,You think nobody will notice?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.62,0:16:18.33,Default,,0,0,0,,But we both know someone\Nwho will, Colonel Zol!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.69,0:16:19.89,Default,,0,0,0,,The Kamen Rider?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.53,0:16:24.95,Default,,0,0,0,,If I may, sir...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.95,0:16:30.05,Default,,0,0,0,,We will soon launch an attack on Kamen Rider\Nto prove the skills of Junior Shocker.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.58,0:16:43.92,Default,,0,0,0,,There haven't been any\Ndisappearances since then.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.58,0:16:48.80,Default,,0,0,0,,We won't be able to locate Goro\Nuntil Shocker makes a move.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.80,0:16:50.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.37,0:16:54.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Goro!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.81,0:16:56.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Where have you gone?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.52,0:16:57.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Calm down.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.69,0:17:00.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Getting frustrated won't help us.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.53,0:17:02.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Hayato.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.52,0:17:03.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.51,0:17:05.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.64,0:17:09.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm all alone in life.\NNo parents, no siblings...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.98,0:17:11.05,Default,,0,0,0,,So...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.61,0:17:14.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd begun to think of Goro\Nas my real little brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.44,0:17:20.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel the same way, Taki.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.49,0:17:21.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.60,0:17:23.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I suppose you would...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.28,0:17:26.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.69,0:17:29.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Footsteps!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.17,0:17:43.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Goro!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.15,0:17:46.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Look out, Taki!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.67,0:17:51.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Goro!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.59,0:17:53.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh no! Goro's been hypnotized!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.73,0:17:55.42,Default,,0,0,0,,His eyes... Look at his eyes!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.68,0:18:00.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Goro's joined Shocker?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.64,0:18:09.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn... there's nothing we can do!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.80,0:18:12.22,Default,,0,0,0,,There must be a Shocker\Ncommander controlling them.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.22,0:18:14.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I know... Mukadelas!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.06,0:18:24.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Junior Shocker... Go forth! Fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.64,0:18:32.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's make a break for it, Taki!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.85,0:18:33.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.15,0:18:44.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Taki. You keep them locked in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.41,0:18:45.44,Default,,0,0,0,,What about you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.44,0:18:46.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to find Mukadelas!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.31,0:18:54.16,Default,,0,0,0,,You idiots! Blow up the door!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.66,0:19:03.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop it! What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.96,0:19:09.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I hear it...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.48,0:19:12.98,Default,,0,0,0,,With my hearing ten times\Nstronger than a normal person,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.98,0:19:14.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I hear it clearly!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.15,0:19:16.26,Default,,0,0,0,,It's coming from...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.90,0:19:17.90,Default,,0,0,0,,that mountain!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.15,0:19:22.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Transform!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.79,0:19:39.02,Default,,0,0,0,,It's time to finish what we started!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.48,0:19:42.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider Power!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.57,0:20:16.54,Default,,0,0,0,,What now, Rider?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.69,0:21:23.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.61,0:21:40.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider Throw!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.75,0:21:45.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Get back! I'm lighting it!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.76,0:21:50.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop it! Don't do this!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.77,0:22:21.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.75,0:22:38.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Mukadelas is dead...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.83,0:22:42.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Has the Junior Shocker\Nplan fallen through?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.44,0:22:57.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.08,0:23:00.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.04,0:23:04.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.08,0:23:05.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.17,0:23:07.65,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on here?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.14,0:23:09.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Everything's all right now, Taki.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.70,0:23:21.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Goodbye! Goodbye!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.03,0:23:26.31,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Shocker's plan to exploit\Nthe children failed,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.16,0:23:29.63,Narrator,,0,0,0,,and these cheerful kids\Nwere safe once more.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.63,0:23:33.30,Narrator,,0,0,0,,But Shocker would already be\Nformulating their next move!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.21,0:23:40.76,Cont,,0,50,0,,{\blur.8\fad(0,400)}To be continued
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.17,0:23:43.01,NEP AND TITLE,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\4aFF\bord0\b1\fs67.5\fnCalibri\pos(499.031,466.481)}Next Episode Preview
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.17,0:23:44.82,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The next assassin sent by Shocker\NHQ to kill our Kamen Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.82,0:23:46.44,Narrator,,0,0,0,,is the monstrous Mogurang!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.44,0:23:50.46,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Shocker is plotting to use mole people\Nto cause pandemonium at Tokyo Bay.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.46,0:23:55.85,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider's fight with Mogurang unfolds\Nat the All-Japan Motocross Championships.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.85,0:24:00.17,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Join us next week for more Kamen Rider\Nin "Underground Monster Mogurang!"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.22,0:24:01.10,NEP AND TITLE,,0,0,0,,{\fscx100\fs125\bord0\fnCienfuegos\4aFF\b1\pos(497.167,670.389)}Underground Monster Mogurang!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.17,0:24:11.01,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,He came here on a storm...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.59,0:24:13.60,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Who is he? Who is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.60,0:24:15.56,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Who is this man of storms,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.56,0:24:18.60,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,who sends the villains scattering?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.10,0:24:20.98,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.98,0:24:22.85,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,His mask stands for justice!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.85,0:24:24.65,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Start it up! Rev it up!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.65,0:24:26.07,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Get that engine running!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.44,0:24:28.49,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Give me top speed, Cyclone!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.53,0:24:34.20,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Hit them with all of your anger!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.20,0:24:37.79,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Put an end to Shocker's evil!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.79,0:24:41.46,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider! Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.87,0:24:45.63,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider!
Comment: 0,0:03:21.53,0:03:26.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Mukadelas' Monster School